Package: supertrend
Type: Package
Title: SuperTrend Indicator and Signals for 'quantmod'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Lars", family = "Bernhardsson",
                  email = "cran.sherry228@passinbox.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Computes the SuperTrend technical indicator (Olivier Seban,
    based on Average True Range) and extracts long/short entry and exit
    signals from trend flips. Provides a 'quantmod'-idiomatic chart
    overlay so the indicator can be added to existing 'chartSeries' plots
    in the same way as 'addBBands' or 'addMACD'. The SuperTrend
    calculation matches the conventions used by major charting platforms
    such as TradingView.
